        <name>ZSOCK_TLS_CIPHERSUITE_LIST</name>
        <initializer>3</initializer>
        <briefdescription>
<para>Socket option to select ciphersuites to use. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>It accepts and returns an array of integers with IANA assigned ciphersuite identifiers. If not set, socket will allow all ciphersuites available in the system (mbedTLS default behavior). </para>
        </detaileddescription>
        <inbodydescription>
