<para>Read-only socket option to read a ciphersuite chosen during TLS handshake. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>It returns an integer containing an IANA assigned ciphersuite identifier of chosen ciphersuite. </para>
        </detaileddescription>
